<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قالَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> ضمْرةُ، عنْ قادِمِ بنِ مَيْسورٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
